<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200626/edcb003898264950b01c2b0eed4e8021.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">张同禄景泰蓝辉煌同路大富贵赏盘</span></img></p>
